  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.5">
<l>uyntu pōnteṉ ṉulappilāta ventīviṉai kaḷai nācañ ceytuṉa</l>
<l>tantami laṭimai yaṭaintēṉ viṭuvēṉō</l>
<l>vaintu paim talai yāṭara vaṇaimēvip pāṟkaṭal yōka nittirai</l>
<l>cintai ceyta ventā yuṉṉaic cintai ceytu ceytē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Escaping completely, destroying my undiminuishing hot fiery karma,</l>
<l>I reached your endless servantship – will I let go [of you]? –</l>
<l>constantly having you in [my] thoughts, our father who has thoughts</l>
<l>in yogic posture on the milk ocean, resting on the serpent bed whose five hooded heads move.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
